aterm-xml 
---------

This package contains the source code for aterm2xml and xml2aterm.

requirements
------------

You need to download and install libxml2 from:
http://www.xmlsoft.org

Also a recent version of the ATerm library is needed:
http://www.cwi.nl/projects/MetaEnv/aterm

configuration
-------------

./configure --prefix=<prefix> --with-libxml2=`xml2-config --prefix`

building and installing
-----------------------

> gmake all 
> gmake install 
> gmake check

